<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="他将中国文化融入世界建筑：顶尖设计师贝聿铭" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393874" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-yx-20201029-56.jpg" width="800" height="600" /></span></p>
